Script,GibOcW4
setDealerCode(`

/*
South opens 1C, 1D, or 1H and West overcalls at the 1-level in a 4-card suit.

convention-card: 21GF-GIB
auction-filter: Auction.....\n1[CDH]

*/

dealer south

Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Predict-Opening-1-Bid
# Defines oneClub, oneDiamond, and oneHeart
#Import,https://github.com/ADavidBailey/Practice-Bidding-Scenarios/blob/main/script/Total-Points-West
# Defines wTP

# Define suits suitable for 4-card overcall
wAS = hascard(west,AS)
wKS = hascard(west,KS)
wQS = hascard(west,QS)
wJS = hascard(west,JS)
wTS = hascard(west,TS)
w9S = hascard(west,9S)

wAH = hascard(west,AH)
wKH = hascard(west,KH)
wQH = hascard(west,QH)
wJH = hascard(west,JH)
wTH = hascard(west,TH)
w9H = hascard(west,9H)

wAD = hascard(west,AD)
wKD = hascard(west,KD)
wQD = hascard(west,QD)
wJD = hascard(west,JD)
wTD = hascard(west,TD)
w9D = hascard(west,9D)

# AKxx，AQJx，AQTx，AQ9x，AJT9，KQJx，or KQTx
wS4 = (wAS and wKS) or (wAS and wQS and (wJS or wTS or w9S)) or (wAS and wJS and wTS and w9S) or (wKS and wQS and (wJS or wTS))
wH4 = (wAH and wKH) or (wAH and wQH and (wJH or wTH or w9H)) or (wAH and wJH and wTH and w9H) or (wKH and wQH and (wJH or wTH))
wD4 = (wAD and wKD) or (wAD and wQD and (wJD or wTD or w9D)) or (wAD and wJD and wTD and w9D) or (wKD and wQD and (wJD or wTD))
wss = (wS4 and wH4) or (wS4 and wD4) or (wH4 or wD4) 

hxC = clubs(west)==2 and hcp(west,clubs)>0
hxH = hearts(west)==2 and hcp(west,hearts)>0
hxS = spades(west)==2 and hcp(west,spades)>0
hxD = diamonds(west)==2 and hcp(west,diamonds)>0
hx  = hxC or hxH or hxS or hxD

cOC = oneClub    and (wD4 or wH4 or wS4) and clubs(west)==3    and hcp(west,clubs)<2
dOC = oneDiamond and (wH4 or wS4)        and diamonds(west)==3 and hcp(west,diamonds)<2
hOC = oneHeart   and wS4                 and hearts(west)==3   and hcp(west,hearts)<2
wOvercalls = (cOC or dOC or hOC) and hcp(west)>10 and hcp(west)<15 and shape(west,any 4432) and not hx

sOpens = hcp(south)>11 and hcp(south)<15

# Now do it.
sOpens and wOvercalls


action
average "1C   " 100 * cOC,
average "1D   " 100 * dOC,
average "1H   " 100 * hOC,

`, "S", false)
Script

Button,GIB OC w/4-cards,\n\
--- GIB overcalls in a 4-card suit\n\
South opens and West makes a 1-level overcall with a 4-card suit.\n\
The required suit quality is AKxx，AQJx，AQTx，AQ9x，AJT9，KQJx，KQTx，or better.\n\
West's shape is 4432 with 3-cards in opener's suit and West's HCP is 11-14\n\
West does not have Ax，Kx，or Qx.\n\
%GibOcW4%